{"tid":1626224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地每個人都係文宣組","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:23:31.000Z","uid":55739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4adbab7227ad46a0c4a81664662633e96d23357","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"點解個撚個都係講緊交比文宣組？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地個個都係文宣組</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當勇武手足裝修緊果陣，一定會有人圍觀。<br />\n唔該各位和理非，主動少少，主動同圍觀既人傾計解釋，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特別係一啲睇到面有難色既人</span></span><br />\n我地有200萬人 一人解釋一個已經多200萬張文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你做幾多文宣<br />\n都唔會夠人地朋友同佢講一句<br />\n各有各做<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n每個人都可以做多少少</span></span>"},{"pid":"6dbbf9f39ba5a867c36fa1ec41be8fb8c1461b98","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40647c0c245bf677dbdba379d99173cbc5ece93e","tid":1626224,"uid":284104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"[文宣獨行俠] 元朗天水圍抗黨鐵地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"459a94280267a337f72801757cc9518f1a2ead3a","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cd39faa56aa830efc6ce99d5e98a3f36d40d95c","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aca53f06f667ee3c51049851c4ce12f1dcf61fa","tid":1626224,"uid":257293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"裝修有好多種<br />\n其實裝修可以裝成連儂牆<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n貼滿中共紅底黑社會嘅證據<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪，甚至清唔到等佢哋自己換玻璃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72%26oe%3D5E364A79&h=7003ea3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9f0a86c3648db394f0f8c1d3ae7a9229c1e5cbf","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff7ae0697e39cb9f2f8784113d8287516d366cd4","tid":1626224,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c21106dfc32100496575b481fd1c5c693a15ffba","tid":1626224,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"[新職業]牆紙師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625944</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"7b55ab6c2e7c8f9026539e0b4b12932cef045e1d","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"694f42232ce35e230f509c7aa273d1f7c6a0087a","tid":1626224,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbb7709db05ce2aa7520b6b6998ed3469e5e3630","tid":1626224,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befcfdf606a001f0ba6fa2207dfef1b56a5244e0","tid":1626224,"uid"